g.text: Why automation of testing in Microsoft environments matters
Automation of regression testing enables companies to keep up with
paced update cadence by significantly reducing the time
required to test new releases. It allows for quick and reliable verification of
system functionality, ensuring a smooth transition to the latest updates.
Automation helps improve testing coverage by executing a comprehensive suite
of test cases quickly and efficiently. With each update, Dynamics 365 introduces
new features and enhancements that need to be thoroughly tested. Automation
